                  <p>Traditional folk of Canada's Maritimes (Nova Scotia, Prince Edward Island, and New Brunswick).</p>
               </div>
         
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/cape-breton-folk-music/">Cape Breton Folk Music</a>
                  <p>Celtic Folk Music that emerged in Cape Breton, an island at the eastern shore of Nova Scotia, through immigrants from Scotland and Ireland.</p>
               </div>
         
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
