                  <p>Cumbia argentina heavily influenced by Reggaetón and characterized by hard-hitting bass and heavy use of samples and Auto-Tune.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/cumbia-villera/">Cumbia villera</a>
                  <p>Developed in the villa miserias (shanty towns) by the lower classes of Argentina in the early 2000s, featuring basic rhythms and low budget productions combined with lyrics that can be openly sexual or touch on sociopolitical issues.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
