         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/forro-de-favela/">Forró de favela</a>
                  <p>Originating from the outskirts of Fortaleza, with MPB-influenced lyrics and a calmer and more romantic sound.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
