                  <a href="/genre/northern-brazilian-music/">Northern Brazilian Music</a>
                  <p>Regional styles rooted in Northern Brazil, often influenced by Caribbean rhythms and instrumentations, usually with focus on romance, celebrations, the relationship between the man and the Amazon rainforest, and danced in fast and sensual movements.</p>
               </div>
         
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
