               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/carimbo/">Carimbó</a>
                  <p>Originated in rural areas in the state of Pará, danced frenetically to the beat of syncopated drums, with international recognition after its modernization.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
