               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/chicago-school/">Chicago School</a>
                  <p>Predominantly 1990s Post-Rock scene which blends influences from Indie Rock and Jazz with an expanded instrumental palette and a diverse approach to sonic exploration.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/chikipunk/">Chikipunk</a>
                  <p>Peruvian scene of the late 1990s and early 2000s as a new scene of Pop Punk, Melodic Hardcore, Skate Punk, Emo and Nu Metal bands without influences from Rock subterráneo.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
