                  <p>Developed in the 1990s in the United States, incorporating faith-based Christian messages into Hardcore [Punk] music.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/cleveland-punk/">Cleveland Punk</a>
                  <p>Early Punk scene in Cleveland, Ohio during the 1970s and early 1980s.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/clube-da-esquina/">Clube da esquina</a>
                  <p>Brazilian scene from the state of Minas Gerais, mostly active in the 1960s and 1970s.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
