               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/crisalida-sonica/">Crisálida sónica</a>
                  <p>Peruvian scene of the mid-1990s influenced by Shoegaze, Post-Rock, Space Rock Revival, IDM and Ambient.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/dariacore/">Dariacore</a>
                  <p>SoundCloud-based scene developed in the early 2020s, combining prominent vocal samples and distorted, dense production with influences from a wide range of Electronic Dance Music genres, often incorporating musical and visual references to popular media and internet culture.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/darmstadt-school/">Darmstadt School</a>
                  <p>Circle of post-World War II Western European composers of avant-garde Modern Classical, exploring Serialism and other innovations.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/d_c-hardcore/">D.C. Hardcore</a>
                  <p>Influential early Hardcore Punk scene centered around Washington, D.C., originating in the late 1970s.</p>
               </div>
         
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
