               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/revolution-summer/">Revolution Summer</a>
                  <p>Collection of bands coalesced around the goal of rejuvenating the Washington D.C. Hardcore scene in the summer of 1985, creating the early foundations for Post-Hardcore and Emo in the process.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
