                  <p>Mass, youth-driven bohemian scene in Los Angeles in the second half of the 1960s, encompassing genres such as Folk Rock and Psychedelic Rock.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
