               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/madchester/">Madchester</a>
                  <p>Manchester-based eclectic, Dance-infused music and cultural phenomenon from the late 1980s to the early 1990s emphasising drug and rave culture.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/maidcore/">Maidcore</a>
                  <p>Eclectic internet music scene mixing elements of Metal, Post-Rock, and Electronic that originated on Russian social media in the mid-2010s; comprised of artists portrayed as 'maid' characters derived from the Japanese Nijiura imageboard.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
