                  <p>Emerged in late 1970s Minneapolis, characterized by glossy Contemporary R&amp;B-influenced production techniques, angular New Wave-inspired rhythms, and a larger emphasis on electric guitar layers.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
