            <li class="hierarchy_list_item">
               <div class="hierarchy_list_item_details">
                  <a href="/genre/ultra/">Ultra</a>
                  <p>Late 1970s and 1980s Dutch DIY scene of musicians influenced by Post-Punk and experimental Electronic music.</p>
               </div>
         
         
            </li>
         </ul>
                  
         <ul class="hierarchy_list">
